HAPPY BIRTHDAY MUMMY!! @editherivo 
This is one her favorite songs, whenever it comes on she’s up dancing!!! More dancing for you this year mummy!! More fun, more laughter, more light, more love, more life!! I love you sweet mother!! ❤️
It is and will always be an honor to be recognized by my peers. Thank you @sagawards for this on behalf of Ms Aretha Louise Franklin.

Whew!! Another year added to my life, I can not begin to express the gratitude I have for the seconds, minutes, hours, days, weeks, months and years I have been given. I’m grateful for ALL the people who have graced my life with their presence even for a second. I’m grateful to have loved and lost and loved again. I’m grateful for the lessons learned. I’m grateful for dreams deferred that made room for DREAMS realized!! My birthday wish is for you, reading, to have the fullest life!! That’s the kind of life I strive for everyday. FULL LIFE!! X.

I was trying to think of which pictures to to post and which 10 slides I wanted to share, but this video felt like it had all the things I wanted to say. It started as a song about my own personal hurt, it grew into a song of love because I was able to release it for those who have experienced loss. This song marks huge moments in my life, every time I’ve been brave enough to sing it, it means something new, it is a celebration of growth, a claiming of love, an acceptance of humanity, it is a gift from people I care deeply about (@williamfwells, @anthonyramosofficial), it’s the space for tears, a space for breath, a space to smile. It’s a song I’m so proud of, it is honest and it is so quintessentially me. 2021 gave me all of this, massive highs, low lows and beautiful in betweens, that’s this song. 

So as we come to 2022, I pray you find the song that gives you all the things you need to keep moving forward, even when it’s hard. 

Here’s to music that makes us feel, hears to music that makes us heal, here’s to music that holds us tight just when we need it. 

Also just in case it’s not clear my mummy  is ALIVE and well, she walks over 20000 steps a day 😩. 

I love you, I hope you love you more. 
Happy New Year!

latestPosts.caption: Please allow the best of me to give you the Worst of Me. 🕊️❤️‍🩹 Out now. Enjoy.

Welcome to another journey in my life.
If you know me, you know it’s pour my heart out time. If you’re new here welcome, sometimes I lay my heart on my sleeve for you. 
Music is my love
Music is my second language 
Music is a way for you to get know me, all the joys and pains and everything in between. I am so excited and grateful that I get to share a LOT more with you. 
Over the next few months you are going to get pieces of my heart, I’m honored to share it. The first piece is Replay and it comes to you with love today/tonight/tomorrow. 
For my sweethearts who are in their heads.
For the babies whose thoughts are sometimes too loud. 
For my anxious angels.
For all of you who are trying to work it all out. 
We are all a work in progress. 
This is for you. 
For us. 
Love Cynthia
